(4167, 760, 6, 'har-gul-saan-guftagu-men-guzrandi-gharri-aahe', 'har gul saan guftagu men guzrandi gharri aahe,\r\nwaau jo thadheero Aa, ghum maan ghumee aayo,\r\ntun ddakhanr dde ddis khanri hoo\'a ute kharri aahe,\r\nrut je raqeeban men tun peer wajh paka pahnja,\r\nwag wath wichheray je, je ajaan jarri aahe,\r\nmaan azal khan aajiyan jaa git\'a piyo jahin laai likhaan,\r\nsamhun saa paee ache، laarr khan larry aahe.', NULL, 'en', '2024-03-22 02:46:37', '2024-03-22 02:46:37', NULL),
