(4321, 884, 40, 'muhaanry-jian-jawani-men', 'muhaanry jian jawani men\r\nnadi ean aarkherian men\r\nnadi jaa nainr jal thal haa\r\nnadi khe neer neenan men\r\nnadi khe bhaakrun men hui\r\njawani mirbahran je\r\nnadi khe chelah te aayaa\r\nsadaa ho waar suhnri\'a jaa\r\nnadi khe neengrian hod\'yo\r\nnadi kaya aar jobhan jaa\r\nnadi watt paar jobhan jaa\r\nnadi watt chelah sanharri aen\r\nnadi watt mookryon chanryun\r\nnadi khe aarson morray\r\njawani jjnr ta wai borray!\r\nnadi be anat hoondy hui\r\nnadi hui manjri chhorri\r\nnadi watt sang aanbho huaa\r\nnadi watt laarr sareen saan\r\nnadi watt laal laharyoon\r\nnadi khe chhaj men chhirryoan\r\nnadi te masat huaa chhora\r\nnadi khe seendh men gaeyoon\r\nwajayaoon wanasali men pai\r\nnadi khe khawaab indaa huaa\r\nnadi saan tind muhanre je\r\nnadi hi lodd chorai\r\nnadi watt nindd\'a muhanre je\r\nnadi jo samund\' neeray saan\r\nsadaa ho sik jo naatoo\r\nnadi khe bhar te beehi\r\nmuhanre waah jo gaato\r\nnadi hui maau jeejal jian\r\nnadi insaaf saan keddo\r\nwirhanre wangyaan men paee!\r\nnadi watt kunwaar laadaa huaa\r\nnadi paee aarti laathi\r\nnadi hui bararre waangy\r\nnadi lay peengh batelo\r\nnadi hui hyderi melo\r\nnadi hui methh milaapo\r\nwichhorro bhar ddei guzaryas\r\nnadi thi neth niyaapo\r\nbakhyal hui banhrryan men jjnr\r\nnadi saan meer munharn khe\r\nkadahn jaa kaklan men thi\r\nsutee thi nindd\'a beeriyan men\r\nheanr saa band beeriyan men\r\nmusaafir qed thi wei \r\nmusaafir qed thi wei', NULL, 'en', '2024-03-22 13:51:26', '2024-03-22 13:51:26', NULL),
