(4446, 899, 36, 'awhan-hi-puchhiyo-paee-uhe-keru-aahin', 'awhan hi puchhiyo paee, uhe ker\'u aahin?\r\nje jhandan saan aayaa, samoondan te chahyaa\r\nzamanan je oondah khe naon chhirak bakhshyo \r\nhawaun je hath te b ddeyaa jalaya\r\nhi pahinje watan men kayal gair aahin!\r\nawhan hi puchhiyo paee, uhe ker\'u aahin?\r\nbudhayoon thaa saahib, thaa bilkul budhayoon\r\nta piryan ugharaa uhe baaru kanhin jaa\r\nta kanhin joon mathan men mitti piyal hi maaon\r\nhi kanhin jo luttyal qaaflo Aa shahar men\r\nhi ‘ baghdad baghdad ’ chawndarr hawaaun\r\nkarayoon thaa taaruf, sabhan jo karayoon\r\nhi mitti\'a te marandarr e mahmeer aahin!\r\nawhan hi puchhiyo paee, uhe ker\'u aahin?\r\nmisar khan b agg\'u men, sumeriyaan khan pehreen\r\nhunan e zamane khe tahzeeb aachay\r\nhunan e ho kirran jo resham  sanbhalyo\r\nhunan e zamane je ogharr dhakaai\r\nhunan e ta malmal jo kapro b thaahiyo\r\nhunan e shahar jo tasawur ddino ho\r\nhunan surr aen sangeet mazhab banraayu\r\nhunan mor poojiya \r\naen porhaiyat dhhagaan khe muqdas banraayu\r\naen mohan darro pirn hunan e ho thaahiyo!\r\nna talwar, barrchhi, na bhaalaa banraya\r\nhunan jug sajji lay ujaala banraya\r\nruggo chher thahy, aen bureenddo thaahiyo\r\naen ‘ samabara ’ saan gadd\'u faqat raqas peeto\r\nfaqat piyaar gaayu!\r\nhi vedan jaa khalq, hi jal jaa poojari\r\nhunan e zamane je oondah dhikare!\r\nhi sadaa, hi maasooman, mitti\'a jaa manhun\r\nbaraabar hunan jaa ggara peer aahin!\r\nawhan hi puchhiyo paee, uhe ker\'u aahin?\r\nhunan je ghuran khe lagyun kalh baahyoon\r\nmazaran te, takeen te thiyun hin charrhayun\r\nhi patt soon jahirraa khasya wiya hunan khan\r\nmuqdas pahaarran joon thiyun hin kattayun\r\nhi wars nadiyan jaa, guttar maan thaa piyan,\r\nhi kirran khan bad\'tar hayaati thaa jian\r\nkhazaanan jaa maalik, panan thaa bachan saan\r\npaki te wiya maarya, kuthaa wiya kachan saan\r\nhi malhar ggain aen bukh thaa upaaen\r\nmuhabat thaa pokhaan aen dokhaa thaa khaain\r\nhunan saan musalsal thiyaa an\'dher aahin!\r\nawhan hi puchhiyo paee, uhe ker\'u aahin?\r\nna mangol, taataar, sasani puchhjo,\r\nbehaari, na burmi, na bangali puchhjo,\r\nna qaasim je olaad khan ko puchhanro\r\nna angrezi je putt hilaali\'a khan puchhjo\r\nbaraabar, bilaa\'shaq awheen aahiyo munsif\r\nso asali watan je e waali\'a khan puchhjo\r\njo tahan saan e insaaf jaa weer aahin!\r\nawhan hi puchhiyo paee, uhe ker\'u aahin!!?', NULL, 'en', '2024-03-23 04:41:15', '2024-03-23 04:41:15', NULL),
